{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c609b63b-f963-4872-949c-bb83d7f0ad37","content":"## The Problem\n\n**.NET 9+ MAUI Android requires JDK 21**, but you have JDK 17. The Android build tooling in .NET 9 (and later) raised the minimum from 17 to 21.\n\n## The Fix\n\nInstall JDK 21 and update `JAVA_HOME`:\n\n```bash\nbrew install --cask temurin@21\nexport JAVA_HOME=$(/usr/libexec/java_home -v 21)\n```\n\nAdd the `export` line to your `~/.zshrc` (or `~/.bash_profile`) to persist it.\n\nThen verify:\n\n```bash\njava -version   # should show 21.x\ndotnet build -t:Run -f net9.0-android\n```\n\nAlternatively, you can set it per-project in your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <JavaSdkDirectory>/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/temurin-21.jdk/Contents/Home</JavaSdkDirectory>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"736ab43f-77e6-4a69-ab9a-0cfc0342188b","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on macOS with a .NET MAUI Android build failing with a Java-related error. They have Adoptium Temurin JDK 17.0.12 installed and JAVA_HOME points to it.\n\nThe common issue here is that .NET MAUI / Android SDK requires a specific JDK version. Let me think about what's likely wrong:\n\n1. .NET MAUI Android builds use the Android SDK build tools, which have specific JDK requirements.\n2. As of .NET 8+, the Android SDK requires JDK 17, which they have.\n3. However, a very common issue on macOS is that JAVA_HOME might not be set correctly for the build process, or the path format might be wrong.\n\n\n4. But actually, the real culprit might be that they're using .NET 9 MAUI, which requires JDK 21 instead of JDK 17. That would explain why their build is failing despite having the right JDK installed.\n\nThe solution would be to upgrade to JDK 21 using a package manager, then configure the build to point to the correct Java home directory or set the MSBuild property for the Java SDK location.","outputTokens":977,"requestId":"080E:3EF0C4:A08BDC:BA64C9:69F2A865"},"id":"0513107a-d231-417e-9a7f-0bbf47da830e","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:55:19.477Z","parentId":"9c0ff173-4363-46dd-a970-64391736af4b"}
